President Donald J. Trump is focused on building, creating, and growing more products in the United States using American labor, goods, and determination. He believes that when products are made in the USA, the profits, revenue, and jobs stay within the country. President Trump is proud to showcase the hard work of American producers and is working to strengthen the requirements for buying American-made products. He is also focused on restoring American manufacturing by bringing factories back to life and promoting the well-being of blue-collar workers.